{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ku8UMCYqVzkEcioeViQDyn","type":"tool_result","content":"70\tlater tiers race the index and fail dependency resolution.\n71\t\n72\t## Sibling-package co-tagging\n73\t\n74\tPer REQ-048, `fathomdb-embedder-api` and `fathomdb-embedder` carry the\n75\tsame git tag as the workspace release even though `fathomdb-embedder-api`\n76\truns on its own version axis. The tag prefix is workspace (Axis W);\n77\t`fathomdb-embedder-api` records its independent version inside the tag\n78\tcommit via its `Cargo.toml`.\n79\t\n80\t## Post-publish smoke\n81\t\n82\tPer `feedback_release_verification`, \"green CI + published wheel\" is not\n83\tdone. Release-evidence sweep installs the published wheel from PyPI and\n84\truns an end-to-end open + close + exit smoke before the release is\n85\tdeclared signed. Equivalent npm smoke applies for `@fathomdb/...`\n86\tpublishes. Crate publishes are smoked via `cargo install fathomdb-cli`\n87\tfollowed by `fathomdb doctor check-integrity --json` against a fresh\n88\tfixture database.\n89\t\n90\t## Sources\n91\t\n92\t- `dev/plans/ci-deferred.md` enumerates the pre-0.6.0 workflows being\n93\t  restored.\n94\t- `ADR-0.6.0-crate-topology` (incl. 2026-04-27 sibling amendment + 2026-05-11\n95\t  CLI-via-facade amendment) owns the crate set.\n96\t- `ADR-0.6.0-embedder-protocol` owns the `fathomdb-embedder-api` trait\n97\t  stability posture.\n98\t- REQ-047, REQ-048, REQ-049, REQ-050, REQ-052.\n99\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"461792b1-c5f8-4800-9416-9dfcbd8f629a","uuid":"a4581261-6895-4494-86f9-3b49f6812080","timestamp":"2026-05-17T17:39:58.304Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/tmp/fdb-11d-release-workflow-20260517T145932Z/dev/design/release.md","content":"later tiers race the index and fail dependency resolution.\n\n## Sibling-package co-tagging\n\nPer REQ-048, `fathomdb-embedder-api` and `fathomdb-embedder` carry the\nsame git tag as the workspace release even though `fathomdb-embedder-api`\nruns on its own version axis. The tag prefix is workspace (Axis W);\n`fathomdb-embedder-api` records its independent version inside the tag\ncommit via its `Cargo.toml`.\n\n## Post-publish smoke\n\nPer `feedback_release_verification`, \"green CI + published wheel\" is not\ndone. Release-evidence sweep installs the published wheel from PyPI and\nruns an end-to-end open + close + exit smoke before the release is\ndeclared signed. Equivalent npm smoke applies for `@fathomdb/...`\npublishes. Crate publishes are smoked via `cargo install fathomdb-cli`\nfollowed by `fathomdb doctor check-integrity --json` against a fresh\nfixture database.\n\n## Sources\n\n- `dev/plans/ci-deferred.md` enumerates the pre-0.6.0 workflows being\n  restored.\n- `ADR-0.6.0-crate-topology` (incl. 2026-04-27 sibling amendment + 2026-05-11\n  CLI-via-facade amendment) owns the crate set.\n- `ADR-0.6.0-embedder-protocol` owns the `fathomdb-embedder-api` trait\n  stability posture.\n- REQ-047, REQ-048, REQ-049, REQ-050, REQ-052.\n","numLines":30,"startLine":70,"totalLines":99}}}
